# Place your Claude OAuth token here.
# Copy this file to .auth-token (gitignored) in each workspace folder,
# or place one .auth-token at the org template root to share across all workspaces.
#
# To get your token:
#   security find-generic-password -s "Claude Code-credentials" -w | python3 -c "import sys,json; print(json.load(sys.stdin).get('claudeAiOauth',{}).get('accessToken',''))"
